# GrowthPilot AI — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your real API keys.
# NEVER commit .env.local to version control.
# This file (.env.example) is safe to commit — it contains only placeholder values.

# ── AI Provider (choose one) ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Option 1: OpenAI  (model: gpt-4o-mini)
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Option 2: Google Gemini  (model: gemini-2.0-flash)
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# ── Notes ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# • Only one key is needed. If both are set, OpenAI takes priority.
# • If neither key is set, the app uses realistic mock responses automatically.
# • Keys are read exclusively in lib/ai/client.ts (server-side only).
# • Keys are NEVER exposed to the browser or sent to the frontend.
# • Do NOT prefix these with NEXT_PUBLIC_ — that would expose them publicly.
